title: super temple
review: An important landmark in Agra, the Bageshwarnath Temple is popular among devotees all through the year. During festivals, the temple is beautifully decorated and lit up and becomes the hub of celebrations.

title: Bag nath temple
review: A must visit place with a combo of spirituali and history.spirtuality cos of shivji temple and history cos it is the same place where 40000 people gathered in 1921 against kuli begar tax.It was the  beginning of freedom movement from uttrakhand.A sangam of saryu and gomti is also there.
